<a:B_SakuraFlower:1083204292602773645> **__Want to Find a date faster?__**
Enter matchmaking queue to get matched on speed dates with other singles! Once we've found a match you'll be notified in DM and if both of you approves, it's a date!
<a:B_SakuraFlower:1083204292602773645> **__Some useful information__**
<a:whte_serinityecekrainbow:1083579247727214713>  You must complete your <#1081002119294894160> to enter the queue!
<a:whte_serinityecekrainbow:1083579247727214713>  You must have a completed profile in <#1081002352070381639> to be matched!
<a:whte_serinityecekrainbow:1083579247727214713>  You won't get matched while you're offline!
<a:whte_serinityecekrainbow:1083579247727214713>  You can only get matched once every hour!
<a:whte_serinityecekrainbow:1083579247727214713>  Bot will match you based on your preferences roles!
<a:B_SakuraFlower:1083204292602773645> **Press the buttons below to enter/leave matchmaking queue!**
